  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Clinical trial evaluating efficacy of bowel cleansing solutions in patients with Inflammatory&#xD;
      Bowel Disease.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Simple blind, randomized study evaluating efficacy of 1LPEG vs 2L PEG vs 2L sodium&#xD;
      picosulfate in bowel cleansing of patients diagnosed of Inflammatory Bowel Disease undergoing&#xD;
      diagnostic or follow-up routine colonoscopy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
